## Example Code Generation

### Button
```tsx
import Button from '@mui/material/Button';

<Button
  variant="contained"
  color="primary"
  sx={{ mt: 2 }}
  aria-label="Submit form"
>
  Submit
</Button>
```

### Form Field
```tsx
import TextField from '@mui/material/TextField';

<TextField
  label="Email"
  type="email"
  required
  fullWidth
  helperText="We'll never share your email"
  aria-describedby="email-helper"
  error={!!errors.email}
  helperText={errors.email || "Enter your email address"}
/>
```

### Responsive Grid
```tsx
import Grid from '@mui/material/Grid';

<Grid container spacing={3}>
  <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={4}>
    {/* Mobile: full, Tablet: half, Desktop: third */}
  </Grid>
</Grid>
```

### Card with Avatar and Badge
```tsx
import Card from '@mui/material/Card';
import Avatar from '@mui/material/Avatar';
import Badge from '@mui/material/Badge';

<Card elevation={1}>
  <CardHeader
    avatar={
      <Badge badgeContent={4} color="error">
        <Avatar src={user.avatar}>{user.initials}</Avatar>
      </Badge>
    }
    title={user.name}
    subheader={user.role}
  />
  <CardContent>...</CardContent>
</Card>
```

## Quality Checklist

Before suggesting code, ensure:
- [ ] Uses CDS design tokens (no hard-coded values)
- [ ] Includes ARIA attributes where needed
- [ ] Supports keyboard navigation
- [ ] Has proper color contrast
- [ ] Meets 48px touch target minimum
- [ ] Is responsive (uses breakpoints)
- [ ] Uses semantic HTML
- [ ] Includes loading states for async actions
- [ ] Has error handling for forms
- [ ] Follows mobile-first approach

## When User Asks About Components

1. Check COMPONENT-INDEX.md for component location
2. Reference the specific DESIGN-SYSTEM-DOCUMENTATION-[COMPONENT].md file
3. Use TOKEN-REFERENCE.md for token values
4. Check PATTERN-LIBRARY.md for integration patterns
5. Generate code following all rules above

## Component Search Keywords

If user mentions:
- "navigation", "menu", "sidebar" → AppBar, Drawer, Menu, BottomNavigation
- "form", "input", "field" → TextField, Checkbox, Radio, Switch, Select
- "button", "click", "action" → Button, IconButton, FAB, LoadingButton
- "card", "content" → Card, Paper, Box
- "list", "items" → List, Table, ImageList
- "loading", "spinner" → Progress, Skeleton, LoadingButton, Backdrop
- "alert", "notification" → Alert, Snackbar, Dialog
- "layout", "grid", "container" → Container, Grid, Stack, Box
- "user", "profile", "avatar" → Avatar, Badge
- "tooltip", "hint", "popup" → Tooltip, Popover

## Quick Token Reference

| Need | Token | Value |
|------|-------|-------|
| Primary color | `primary.main` | #1976d2 |
| Standard padding | `spacing(4)` | 16px |
| Card spacing | `spacing(3)` | 12px |
| Grid gap | `spacing={3}` | 12px |
| Button default | `size="medium"` | 40px |
| Card elevation | `elevation={1}` | Subtle |
| App bar elevation | `elevation={4}` | Standard |
| Border radius | `borderRadius: 1` | 4px |

